            <title>[CASSANDRA-3202] CFMetata.getMergeShardChance returns readRepairChance</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3202</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The summary says it all. Note that &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-3178&quot; title=&quot;Counter shard merging is not thread safe&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-3178&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-3178&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; will hopefully make that option useless. But in the meantime, this breaks the tests in 1.0.0 since read repair chance was set to 0.1 by default (while the test assumes merge_shard_chance is 1), so let&apos;s fix that quickly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
